{
  "info": {
    "name": "Notification Service",
    "description": "# Notification Service\n\nBase URL: `{{notification_service}}` (port `8090`)\n\nHandles in-app notification sending and querying. Notifications are stored in H2 (dev) or MySQL (prod).\n\n## Status enum\n\n- `INFO` \u2014 General information\n- `WARNING` \u2014 Warning or alert\n- `SUCCESS` \u2014 Successful operation\n- `ERROR` \u2014 Error condition\n\nTypes are free-form strings (e.g. `ESTIMATE_READY`, `RECOMMENDATIONS_READY`, `PRICE_ALERT`).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Direct",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Send Notification",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "host": [
                "{{notification_service}}{{api_prefix}}"
              ],
              "raw": "{{notification_service}}{{api_prefix}}/notifications/send",
              "path": [
                "notifications",
                "send"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Sends a notification with `INFO` status.\n\n**Expected:** 201 Created",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": 1,\n  \"type\": \"ESTIMATE_READY\",\n  \"content\": \"Your budget estimate for build #5 is ready.\",\n  \"status\": \"INFO\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Notification Warning",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "host": [
                "{{notification_service}}{{api_prefix}}"
              ],
              "raw": "{{notification_service}}{{api_prefix}}/notifications/send",
              "path": [
                "notifications",
                "send"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Sends a notification with `WARNING` status.\n\n**Expected:** 201 Created",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": 1,\n  \"type\": \"COMPATIBILITY_WARNING\",\n  \"content\": \"Build #5 has incompatible components: CPU socket LGA1700 does not match motherboard socket AM5.\",\n  \"status\": \"WARNING\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
